接口 Deque

  • 所有已知实现类:

    public interface Deque
    Represents a Deque of Integers.

        Boolean isEmpty()
        Check if the deque id empty.
        返回:

      • size

        Integer size()
        The number of element in deque.
        返回:
        0 for empty deque; number of elements in non empty deque

      • addFirst

        Deque addFirst(Integer element)
        throws UnsupportedOperationException
        Add n to the head of the deque.
        参数:
        element - the new integer to be added
        返回:
        same deque with n added
        抛出:
        UnsupportedOperationException - with appropriate message if calling on a non empty FIFO deque or an empty FIFO deque

      • addLast

        Deque addLast(Integer element)
       throws UnsupportedOperationException
        Add nto rhe tail of the deque.
        参数:
        element - the new integer to be added
        返回:
        same deque with n added
        抛出:
        UnsupportedOperationException - with appropriate message if calling on an empty LIFO deque or a non empty LIFO deque

      • removeFirst

        Deque removeFirst()
           throws IllegalOperationException
        Remove the first integer of a deque.
        返回:
        the same deque with the first element removed
        抛出:
        IllegalOperationException - if calling on any empty deque

      • peek

        Integer peek()
      throws Error
        Get the deque's first element.
        返回:
        the first element of the deque
        抛出:
        Error - if calling on any empty deque
